{
  "id": "628906c509ef09001d2c3488",
  "title": "百人一首の断簡を読んでみる",
  "created": 1653147334,
  "updated": 1688702022,
  "lines": [
    {
      "id": "628906c509ef09001d2c3488",
      "text": "百人一首の断簡を読んでみる",
      "userId": "60508ed36a7abc00235e90c0",
      "created": 1653147334,
      "updated": 1653147334
    },
    {
      "id": "628906c75e90c00000f778fd",
      "text": "from [2022/05/21]",
      "userId": "60508ed36a7abc00235e90c0",
      "created": 1653147334,
      "updated": 1653147334
    },
    {
      "id": "628906c75e90c00000f778fe",
      "text": "百人一首の断簡を読んでみる",
      "userId": "60508ed36a7abc00235e90c0",
      "created": 1653147334,
      "updated": 1653147334
    },
    {
      "id": "628906c75e90c00000f778ff",
      "text": ">[https://twitter.com/hitomaroeiku/status/1527932090326691840?s=20&t=3-p0jcglKfwn_nYPyqO5DQ @hitomaroeiku]: 色紙のようにみえますが、元禄頃写の[枡形本]『[百人一首]』の[断簡]です。平安から鎌倉期にかけて用いられた[蝋箋]（ろうせん）を、江戸時代に復活させた紙を用いています。版木に胡粉を塗った紙を重ねて、硬い物で擦り、[摩擦]で模様を擦り出しています。模様部分が蝋を塗ったようにみえこの名があります。",
      "userId": "62a91a7a083437001de60035",
      "created": 1653147334,
      "updated": 1660782918
    },
    {
      "id": "628906c75e90c00000f77900",
      "text": ">[https://gyazo.com/50f3bd68d31802ca017ba8aa1d105463]",
      "userId": "5ef2bdebb60650001e1280f0",
      "created": 1653147334,
      "updated": 1688702022
    },
    {
      "id": "628978c35e90c00000abfa2c",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "60508ed36a7abc00235e90c0",
      "created": 1653176513,
      "updated": 1653176513
    },
    {
      "id": "628978bc5e90c00000abfa2b",
      "text": " 綺麗な[写本]だと思う[issac.icon]",
      "userId": "60508ed36a7abc00235e90c0",
      "created": 1653176506,
      "updated": 1653179480
    },
    {
      "id": "628906c75e90c00000f77901",
      "text": " [百人一首を崩し字で読んでみる]でくずし字トレーニングをしていたお陰ですらすら読めた",
      "userId": "60508ed36a7abc00235e90c0",
      "created": 1653147334,
      "updated": 1653147334
    },
    {
      "id": "628906c75e90c00000f77902",
      "text": "  しばらく読んでないとなまる",
      "userId": "60508ed36a7abc00235e90c0",
      "created": 1653147334,
      "updated": 1653147334
    },
    {
      "id": "628906fb5e90c000000265e5",
      "text": " [柿本人麿]の「本」をすごい順序で書いてる[yosider.icon]",
      "userId": "60508ed36a7abc00235e90c0",
      "created": 1653147385,
      "updated": 1653147385
    },
    {
      "id": "628906c75e90c00000f77903",
      "text": " こっちは「足曳」なんだな、ものによって違う[nishio.icon]",
      "userId": "60508ed36a7abc00235e90c0",
      "created": 1653147334,
      "updated": 1653147334
    },
    {
      "id": "628906c75e90c00000f77904",
      "text": "  みなれない「き」が使われている。「春すきて」が漢字ではなくひらがな",
      "userId": "60508ed36a7abc00235e90c0",
      "created": 1653147334,
      "updated": 1653147334
    },
    {
      "id": "628906c75e90c00000f77905",
      "text": "  [変体仮名]一覧になってないけど雰囲気的に「己」の崩れたやつかな？？",
      "userId": "60508ed36a7abc00235e90c0",
      "created": 1653147334,
      "updated": 1653147334
    },
    {
      "id": "628906c75e90c00000f77906",
      "text": "   みなれない「き」とは、春過ぎての「き」です？[issac.icon]",
      "userId": "60508ed36a7abc00235e90c0",
      "created": 1653147334,
      "updated": 1653147334
    },
    {
      "id": "628906c75e90c00000f77907",
      "text": "   すごく崩れた「幾」として読んだ[issac.icon]",
      "userId": "60508ed36a7abc00235e90c0",
      "created": 1653147334,
      "updated": 1653147334
    },
    {
      "id": "628906c75e90c00000f77908",
      "text": "    [https://gyazo.com/a75b1eac0bbc4f8a18844d532dff588b]",
      "userId": "60508ed36a7abc00235e90c0",
      "created": 1653147334,
      "updated": 1653147334
    },
    {
      "id": "628906c75e90c00000f77909",
      "text": "     「き」と「て」",
      "userId": "60508ed36a7abc00235e90c0",
      "created": 1653147334,
      "updated": 1653147334
    },
    {
      "id": "628906c75e90c00000f7790a",
      "text": "　　　　これは難しい…[nishio.icon]",
      "userId": "60508ed36a7abc00235e90c0",
      "created": 1653147334,
      "updated": 1653147334
    },
    {
      "id": "628906c75e90c00000f7790b",
      "text": "　　　　「すきて」になるために下半分の「て」っぽいところは「て」に使われて「き」に対応するのは",
      "userId": "60508ed36a7abc00235e90c0",
      "created": 1653147334,
      "updated": 1653147334
    },
    {
      "id": "628906c75e90c00000f7790c",
      "text": "　　　　　[https://gyazo.com/aabd3c2c2953ff9ea93e0138c9bef8fd]",
      "userId": "60508ed36a7abc00235e90c0",
      "created": 1653147334,
      "updated": 1653147334
    },
    {
      "id": "628906c75e90c00000f7790d",
      "text": "　　　　　だけかと思った",
      "userId": "60508ed36a7abc00235e90c0",
      "created": 1653147334,
      "updated": 1653147334
    },
    {
      "id": "628906c75e90c00000f7790e",
      "text": "　　　　　あ、自分も同じです[issac.icon]",
      "userId": "60508ed36a7abc00235e90c0",
      "created": 1653147334,
      "updated": 1653147334
    },
    {
      "id": "628906c75e90c00000f7790f",
      "text": "　　　　　なるほど[nishio.icon]",
      "userId": "60508ed36a7abc00235e90c0",
      "created": 1653147334,
      "updated": 1653147334
    },
    {
      "id": "628906c75e90c00000f77910",
      "text": "　　　　　[https://gyazo.com/d9b9704aeb4c7bab854cf4caa296ba6b]",
      "userId": "60508ed36a7abc00235e90c0",
      "created": 1653147334,
      "updated": 1653147334
    },
    {
      "id": "628906c75e90c00000f77911",
      "text": "　　　　　　こういうのがもうちょっと汚く書かれたらこうなるか…",
      "userId": "60508ed36a7abc00235e90c0",
      "created": 1653147334,
      "updated": 1653147334
    },
    {
      "id": "628906c75e90c00000f77912",
      "text": "     正直最初見た時は「も(毛)」とか「色」に見えた[issac.icon]",
      "userId": "60508ed36a7abc00235e90c0",
      "created": 1653147334,
      "updated": 1653147334
    },
    {
      "id": "628906c75e90c00000f77913",
      "text": "      あらかじめ知ってないと読めないなー",
      "userId": "60508ed36a7abc00235e90c0",
      "created": 1653147334,
      "updated": 1653147334
    },
    {
      "id": "628906c75e90c00000f77914",
      "text": "　　　　　「夏きにけらし」の「き」もよくわからない[nishio.icon]",
      "userId": "60508ed36a7abc00235e90c0",
      "created": 1653147334,
      "updated": 1653147334
    },
    {
      "id": "628906c75e90c00000f77915",
      "text": "　　　　　　けど、これも同じくめちゃ汚いのか",
      "userId": "60508ed36a7abc00235e90c0",
      "created": 1653147334,
      "updated": 1653147334
    },
    {
      "id": "628906c75e90c00000f77916",
      "text": "　　　　　　これも「幾」に見える[issac.icon][nishio.icon]",
      "userId": "60508ed36a7abc00235e90c0",
      "created": 1653147334,
      "updated": 1653147334
    },
    {
      "id": "628906c75e90c00000f77917",
      "text": "　　　　[https://gyazo.com/ad4c07a7c6d0fc68aa2b5004b60b009b]",
      "userId": "60508ed36a7abc00235e90c0",
      "created": 1653147334,
      "updated": 1653147334
    },
    {
      "id": "628906c75e90c00000f77918",
      "text": "     [https://dl.ndl.go.jp/info:ndljp/pid/852036/5 小倉百人一首 - 国立国会図書館デジタルコレクション]",
      "userId": "60508ed36a7abc00235e90c0",
      "created": 1653147334,
      "updated": 1653147334
    },
    {
      "id": "628984ac5e90c00000c27f14",
      "text": "     ここの「春すぎて」も「き(幾)」",
      "userId": "60508ed36a7abc00235e90c0",
      "created": 1653179562,
      "updated": 1653179628
    },
    {
      "id": "628984f05e90c00000c27f15",
      "text": "      すぐ下の「きに」も「き(幾)」",
      "userId": "60508ed36a7abc00235e90c0",
      "created": 1653179629,
      "updated": 1653179652
    },
    {
      "id": "628985075e90c00000c27f16",
      "text": "      [- [全部違うじゃないですか]]",
      "userId": "60508ed36a7abc00235e90c0",
      "created": 1653179653,
      "updated": 1653179705
    },
    {
      "id": "628906c75e90c00000f77919",
      "text": "    百人一首の綺麗な写本、どっかで見れないかな[issac.icon]",
      "userId": "60508ed36a7abc00235e90c0",
      "created": 1653147334,
      "updated": 1653176486
    },
    {
      "id": "628906c75e90c00000f7791a",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "60508ed36a7abc00235e90c0",
      "created": 1653147334,
      "updated": 1653147334
    },
    {
      "id": "6289785f5e90c00000abfa26",
      "text": ">[https://twitter.com/hitomaroeiku/status/1528130343881961477?s=20&t=cMJUoyPuQ_ak-QML-fG6Pw @hitomaroeiku]: 同じく『百人一首』の断簡ですが、こちらは色と模様の異なる2枚を「[破り継ぎ]」しています。この技法も平安時代のものを模していますが、平安のもののように、継ぎ目がギザギザにはなっていません。",
      "userId": "60508ed36a7abc00235e90c0",
      "created": 1653176412,
      "updated": 1653177396
    },
    {
      "id": "628978605e90c00000abfa28",
      "text": ">[https://gyazo.com/72e17a6da494a9e049efd3bca72ac6f6]",
      "userId": "5ef2bdebb60650001e1280f0",
      "created": 1653176414,
      "updated": 1688702022
    },
    {
      "id": "628980e05e90c00000193134",
      "text": " ちょっとむずい。すらすら読めない[issac.icon]",
      "userId": "60508ed36a7abc00235e90c0",
      "created": 1653178590,
      "updated": 1653178629
    },
    {
      "id": "628978605e90c00000abfa29",
      "text": "  真ん中の歌の「ふる里」の「里」ってこんな文字[https://gyazo.com/fbbcf81256cbb5dfdc61dac4db96b068]なのかしら",
      "userId": "60508ed36a7abc00235e90c0",
      "created": 1653176414,
      "updated": 1653178671
    },
    {
      "id": "628983e85e90c00000c27f10",
      "text": "  [百人一首を崩し字で読んでみる#62821d9faff09e0000d22fb1]と[百人一首を崩し字で読んでみる#62821db2aff09e0000d22fb2]だとまだ読める",
      "userId": "60508ed36a7abc00235e90c0",
      "created": 1653179366,
      "updated": 1653179415
    },
    {
      "id": "6289785f5e90c00000abfa27",
      "text": "   [https://gyazo.com/840f0ac73e89c5362cb71fc0587f57d6][https://gyazo.com/f8be8deb76b9f7c94e35170b92791965]",
      "userId": "60508ed36a7abc00235e90c0",
      "created": 1653176413,
      "updated": 1653179452
    },
